# My Neovim Configuration
- It is full-fledged, way faster than vsc, also looks better
- most shortcuts are managed by which-keys, in ./lua/which-keys.lua

## Install

- Install ripgrep

```shell
cd ~/.config
$ git clone https://github.com/Ji-Xinyou/my.nvim.git nvim # drink some tea
```

In nvim
- run :Lazy
- reopen
- run :TSInstall all
- run :TSUpdate

You are all set.

## MISC
I use ComicShannsMono Nerd Font, I found it really good

